				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">At first glance it might seem like the Neo Geo can update &quot;all of them,&quot; but today I realized that the Neo Geo's oam is 48kB, and that it would take a long time to update all of them.  I don't know if the Neo Geo has DMA or not, nor if I know if you can write during active display, but now I realize that this could be a bottleneck to the system.</div>

